"'''Home'''" 是美國歌手[[菲利·飛力普|菲利·飛力普]]的一首歌曲，也是他的首支單曲，收錄于他的首張錄音室專輯《[[從月亮看世界|從月亮看世界]]》（''The World from the Side of the Moon''）中。歌曲由[[格雷格·霍尔登|格雷格·霍尔登]]和[[德魯·皮爾森_(歌曲創作人)|德鲁·皮尔森]]創作，皮尔森也參與了歌曲的製作。<ref name="THR"/><ref name="pulse"/>  作為《[[美國偶像|美國偶像]]》[[美國偶像_(第十一季)|第11季]]的冠軍，飛力普在該季的決賽（2012年5月22日晚）首次表演了歌曲，在被宣佈為季度冠軍之後又再次表演了歌曲。錄音室版本的 "Home" 于2012年5月23日發行為單曲，并收錄于專輯合輯 ''American Idol Season Finale - Season 11 EP'' 與 ''Journey to the Finale'' 中。<ref name="allmusic"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/home-american-idol-performance/id529347923?i=529348009 |title=Home |publisher=iTunes |date=2012-05-23 |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2016-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924185500/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/home-american-idol-performance/id529347923?i=529348009 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

歌曲發行首週在[[告示牌百強單曲榜|《告示牌》百強單曲榜]]以278,000次的數位下載空降第10名，<ref name="billboard may 2012"/> 這一周也成為《美國偶像》歌曲銷量最高的一周。<ref name="cauldfied">{{cite web |title=Phillip Phillips Makes 'Idol' History as 'Home' Sells 278,000 Downloads |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/485452/phillip-phillips-makes-idol-history-as-home-sells-278000-downloads |last=Caulfield |first=Keith |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-05-30 |accessdate=2012-05-30 |archive-date=2013-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213030128/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/485452/phillip-phillips-makes-idol-history-as-home-sells-278000-downloads |dead-url=no }}</ref> 歌曲也是參賽歌曲中最暢銷的歌曲。<ref name="Yahoo Chart Watch 03-27-2013">{{cite news |title=Chart Watch Extra: Phillips Takes Idol Title |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/chart-watch-extra-phillips-takes-idol-title-145031876.html |last=Grein |first=Paul |work=Chart Watch |publisher=Yahoo |date=2013-03-27 |accessdate=2013-03-27 |archive-date=2013-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130329212511/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/chart-watch-extra-phillips-takes-idol-title-145031876.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 歌曲在美國已獲得超過500萬份銷量。<ref name="us_sales" />

==背景 ==
歌曲由格雷格·霍尔登和德魯·皮爾森共同創作，由[[吉米·洛文|吉米·洛文]]選為飛力普在決賽中演唱的歌曲。據皮爾森說，歌曲原本要給格雷格·霍尔登演唱，但後來被皮爾森的廠牌[[脈搏唱片|脈搏唱片]]拿給了《美國偶像》的冠軍演唱。<ref name="THR">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/american-idol-phillip-phillips-coronation-song-home-327974 |title='American Idol': The Story Behind Phillip Phillips' Coronation Song (Exclusive) |first=Shirley |last=Halperin |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-05-22 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120526002339/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/american-idol-phillip-phillips-coronation-song-home-327974 |archive-date=2012-05-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="pulse">{{cite web |url=http://pulserecordings.com/2012/drew-pearson-phillip-phillips-1.html |title=Drew Pearson / Phillip Phillips – #1 |publisher=Pulse Recording |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622002848/http://pulserecordings.com/2012/drew-pearson-phillip-phillips-1.html |archivedate=2013-06-22 |accessdate=2016-06-23 }}</ref>  皮爾森和霍尔登之前素不相識，但仍然一起創作了這首歌曲，其中歌詞主要由霍尔登負責創作。<ref name="holden">{{cite web|url=http://myblackguitar.com/gregholden/wp-content/uploads/photos/2012/06/Screen-Shot-2012-06-08-at-13.55.101-1024x806.png |title=Home is Where the Cash is |first=Phil |last=Gallo |work=Billboard |date=2012-06-16 }}{{Dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref> 歌曲于2011年11月在皮爾森加州[[伯班克_(加利福尼亚州)|伯班克]]的錄音室創作完成，全程僅用了3小時。原本歌曲有兩大段，但在歌曲創作後的一個月之後將第二大段改為了重複第一大段。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.americansongwriter.com/2012/12/how-did-they-write-that-phillip-phillips-home/ |title=How Did They Write That? Phillip Phillips, "Home" |first=Doug |last=Waterman |work=American Songwriter |date=2012-12-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130108012636/http://www.americansongwriter.com/2012/12/how-did-they-write-that-phillip-phillips-home/ |archivedate=2013-01-08 |accessdate=2016-06-23 }}</ref>  皮爾森指出[[蒙福之子樂團|蒙福之子樂團]]、[[拱廊之火|拱廊之火]]和一些愛爾蘭的樂團是自己創作這首歌的靈感來源。<ref name="THR"/> 皮爾森也錄製了歌曲的樣本唱片，並在他的巡演中表演了這首歌曲，然而他說不會正式發行自己演唱的版本。<ref name="holden"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/phillip-phillips-coronation-song-home-greg-holden-338731 |title=Songwriter Greg Holden Discusses the Success of Phillip Phillips' 'Home' |author=Michele Amabile Angermiller |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-06-18 |access-date=2016-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203124459/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/phillip-phillips-coronation-song-home-greg-holden-338731 |archive-date=2016-02-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>  霍尔登稱，這首歌曲的歌詞描述了一個朋友正處於人生的困境中，但有人讓他知道“有人在這裡幫你”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.browardpalmbeach.com/countygrind/2015/02/singer_greg_holden_is_a_scotsman_with_a_heart_of_gold_interview_2015_charities.php |title=Singer Greg Holden Is a Scotsman With a Heart of Gold |first=Ashley |last=Zimmerman |date=2015-02-12 |work=Broward/Palm Beach New Times |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2015-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212201621/http://blogs.browardpalmbeach.com/countygrind/2015/02/singer_greg_holden_is_a_scotsman_with_a_heart_of_gold_interview_2015_charities.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在歌曲釋出之後，飛力普稱讚歌曲和作者“真的很棒”，但也指出“這不會是我會寫出的東西”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1685717/american-idol-phillip-phillips-home.jhtml. |title=Phillip Phillips won't take credit for 'Home' at 'American Idol' finale |first=Kara |last=Warner |publisher=MTV |date=2012-05-23 |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2019-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017085816/http://www.mtv.com/news/1685717/american-idol-phillip-phillips-home/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他還說他曾希望能夠使用他和他的姐夫共同創作的歌曲 "Drive Me" 為加冕歌曲。<ref>{{Cite journal |url=http://www.accesshollywood.com/phillip-phillips-feeling-right-at-home-during-summer-olympics-coverage_article_68295 |title=Phillip Phillips Feeling Right At Home During Summer Olympics |work=The Associated Press |publisher=Access Hollywood |date=2012-08-09 |journal= |access-date=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012121929/http://www.accesshollywood.com/phillip-phillips-feeling-right-at-home-during-summer-olympics-coverage_article_68295 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在決賽後的採訪中，飛力普說：“這首歌曲理應是我的單曲，（但）它不真是我的單曲，我告訴了他們這真的不是我的單曲。”<ref name="THR2">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/american-idol-phillip-phillips-home-single-329202 |title='American Idol' Champ Phillip Phillips on 'Home': 'I Told Them It's Not My Single' (Video) |author=Michele Amabile Angermiller, Didi Benami |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-05-22 |accessdate=2012-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527004311/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/american-idol-phillip-phillips-home-single-329202 |archive-date=2012-05-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>  又補充道：“我有自己想講述的故事，但我不能（在決賽中）唱自己的歌曲；我們沒有時間。”飛力普自稱他創作歌曲的風格是“爵士和另類搖滾的感覺；不是純搖滾的感覺”<ref name="THR2"/> “在我們錄製唱片之前，我根本沒有時間去做自己、發揚我的音樂風格。”<ref name="billboard_cover">{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1481573/phillip-phillips-the-billboard-cover-story|title='Phillip Phillips' The Billboard Cover Story|first=Phil|last=Gallo|publisher=Billboard|date=2013-01-07|accessdate=2013-01-08|archive-date=2013-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130201135223/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1481573/phillip-phillips-the-billboard-cover-story|dead-url=no}}</ref>  後來他說他“開始與歌曲建立聯繫”，“我開始唱得有點自己的感覺了，彈著吉他演奏（歌曲的）一段，感覺就出來了。”<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/reality-rocks/phillip-phillips-scores-olympic-gold-single-home-171653480.html |title=Phillip Phillips Scores Olympic Gold Single With "Home" |first=Lyndsey |last=Parker |work=Reality Rocks |publisher=Yahoo Music |date=2012-08-01 |accessdate=2012-08-15 |archive-date=2012-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120803034342/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/reality-rocks/phillip-phillips-scores-olympic-gold-single-home-171653480.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==反響==

===樂評===
"Home" 在《美國偶像》表演時即獲得了好評。飛力普成為了當晚唯一一個全體評委起立鼓掌的歌手。[[蘭道爾·大流士·蘭迪·傑克遜|蘭迪·傑克遜]]說：“我愛這首歌曲，我愛你，我愛這首歌曲的製作，我愛仪乐队--這首歌曲有關的一切都非常完美。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/reality-rocks/idol-top-2-recap-battle-opposites-010413950.html |title=‘American Idol’ Top 2 Recap: Battle Of The Opposites |first=Lyndsey |last=Parke |publisher=Yahoo Music |date=2012-05-22 |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2013-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212091156/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/reality-rocks/idol-top-2-recap-battle-opposites-010413950.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[珍妮弗·洛佩兹|珍妮弗·洛佩兹]]說：“菲利演唱的這首歌曲，沒有電台曾播放過的歌曲像這首一樣”。[[史蒂芬·泰勒|史蒂芬·泰勒]]說：“你讓世界成了你的家！”

專業樂評亦稱讚了這首歌曲，稱其為《美國偶像》最佳的加冕歌曲之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://idolator.com/6523632/phillip-phillips-american-idol-coronation-songhome-review |title=Phillip Phillips’ "Home": Review Revue |publisher=Idolator |date= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/idolchatter/post/2012/05/american-idol-weve-got-a-winner/1 |title='American Idol': We've got a winner! |first=Brian |last=Mansfield |work=Idol Chatter |publisher=USA Today |date=2012-05-23 |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2016-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119034348/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/idolchatter/post/2012/05/american-idol-weve-got-a-winner/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 《[[美國歌曲創作人|美國歌曲創作人]]》認為歌曲有“當代流行所具備的所有元素：英國民謠、國歌儀仗隊的風格、傳統的合聲”，并稱飛力普“真是幸運有這樣好的（歌曲）”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.americansongwriter.com/2012/05/the-ballad-of-phillip-phillps/ |title=The Ballad Of Phillip Phillips |author=Marissa R. Moss |work=American Songwriter |date=2012-05-24 |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2016-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321021218/http://americansongwriter.com/2012/05/the-ballad-of-phillip-phillps/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《娱乐周刊》給予歌曲A-的評分，并將歌曲與[[蒙福之子樂團|蒙福之子樂團]]和[[海灣之狐|海灣之狐]]的作品進行比較。雜誌指出“這首凱旋之歌毫無疑問是真人秀中加冕歌曲中有史以來最酷的、最相關的作品。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/05/23/jessica-sanchez-phillip-phillips-single-reviews/ |title='American Idol': Jessica Sanchez's and Phillip Phillips' coronation singles |publisher=EW.com |date=2012-05-23 |author=Grady Smith |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2014-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203014315/http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/05/23/jessica-sanchez-phillip-phillips-single-reviews/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>  《[[秃鹰_(博客)|秃鹰]]》的博客評論亦稱歌曲與蒙福之子樂團的作品相似，并使人想起[[艾德華夏普與無引力樂團|艾德華夏普與無引力樂團]]的那首也叫 "Home"的歌曲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vulture.com/2012/05/american-idol-recap-season-11-finalists-compete.html |title=American Idol Recap: A Shock in the Mire |first=Dave |last=Holmes |publisher=Vulture |date=2012-05-23 |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2016-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203124459/http://www.vulture.com/2012/05/american-idol-recap-season-11-finalists-compete.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 鑒於蒙福之子樂團的風格對歌曲的影響，蒙福之子樂團的成員[[本·洛维特_(英國音樂人)|本·洛维特]]在初聽歌曲時甚至認為這是樂團以前錄製過的作品。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1703729/mumford-and-sons-phillip-phillips-home.jhtml |title=Mumford & Sons On Phillip Phillips' 'Home:' 'Did We Do That? |first=James |last=Montgomery |date=2013-03-15 |work=MTV |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2014-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420031538/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1703729/mumford-and-sons-phillip-phillips-home.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]]》認為歌曲“令人震驚地好 - 尤其是在對於越來越尷尬的《美國偶像》的加冕歌曲來說。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spin.com/articles/american-idol-shocker-phillip-phillips-coronation-song-home-doesnt-suck |title='American Idol' Shocker: Phillip Phillips' Coronation Song 'Home' Doesn't Suck |publisher=Spin |date=2012-05-24 |author=Caryn Ganz |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2015-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213010918/http://www.spin.com/articles/american-idol-shocker-phillip-phillips-coronation-song-home-doesnt-suck/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===商業===
"Home" 空降《告示牌》百強單曲榜第10名，成為4年來第一支空降前十的《美國偶像》單曲。<ref name="billboard may 2012">{{cite web |title=Phillip Phillips Storms Hot 100's Top 10, Gotye Has Year's Longest-Running No. 1 |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/485449/phillip-phillips-storms-hot-100s-top-10-gotye-has-years-longest-running-no-1 |last=Trust |first=Gary |work=Chart Beat |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-05-30 |accessdate=2012-05-30 |archive-date=2013-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529211158/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/485449/phillip-phillips-storms-hot-100s-top-10-gotye-has-years-longest-running-no-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>  歌曲首週獲得了278,000份銷量，打破了有史以來《美國偶像》加冕歌曲最高銷量周的記錄。這一周也是《美國偶像》參賽者歌曲中數字銷量第2高的周，僅次於[[凱莉·克萊森|凱莉·克萊森]]歌曲《[[沒有你，怎麼過|沒有你，怎麼過]]》（''My Life Would Suck Without You''）發行首週的280,000份銷量。<ref name="cauldfied"/>

[[2012年夏季奧運會|2012年夏季奧運會]]播放了歌曲之後，歌曲于8月1日重回《告示牌》百強單曲榜第84名。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/480640/phillip-phillips-home-sales-surge-thanks-to-olympic-gymnasts|title=Phillip Phillips' 'Home' Sales Surge Thanks to Olympic Gymnasts|first=Keith|last=Caulfield|date=2012-08-02|accessdate=2012-08-03|archive-date=2013-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330054635/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/480640/phillip-phillips-home-sales-surge-thanks-to-olympic-gymnasts|dead-url=no}}</ref>  次周，歌曲在3天內又新增了超過105,000份銷量，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/pop2it/2012/08/2012-summer-olympics-american-idol-winner-phillip-phillips-enjoying-his-olympic-fueled-resurgence-to.html |title=2012 Summer Olympics: 'American Idol' winner Phillip Phillips enjoying his Olympic-fueled resurgence to the top of the charts |first=Larry |last=Carroll |publisher=Zap2it |date=2012-08-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120808235756/http://blog.zap2it.com/pop2it/2012/08/2012-summer-olympics-american-idol-winner-phillip-phillips-enjoying-his-olympic-fueled-resurgence-to.html |archivedate=2012-08-08 |accessdate=2016-06-23 }}</ref> 在該周累計增加了228,000份銷量。<ref name="yahoo2aug2012">{{cite news |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-aug-5-2012-songs-phillip-phillips-022224858.html |title=Week Ending Aug. 5, 2012. Songs: Phillip Phillips Is "Home" |first=Paul |last=Grein |work=Chart Watch |publisher=Yahoo Music |date=2012-08-08 |accessdate=2012-08-09 |archive-date=2012-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814011629/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-aug-5-2012-songs-phillip-phillips-022224858.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/480549/rick-ross-scores-fourth-no-1-album-with-god-forgives-i-dont |title=Rick Ross Scores Fourth No. 1 Album with 'God Forgives, I Don't' |first=Keith |last=Caulfield |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-08-08 |accessdate=2012-08-08 |archive-date=2013-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213063729/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/480549/rick-ross-scores-fourth-no-1-album-with-god-forgives-i-dont |dead-url=no }}</ref> 這一周歌曲重回榜單前十，并達到了第9的高位。<ref name="Billboard Aug2012">{{cite news |title=Carly Rae Jepsen Claims Longest Hot 100 No. 1 Run of 2012 |url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/industry/record-labels/carly-rae-jepsen-claims-longest-hot-100-1007780352.story |first=Silvio |last=Pietroluongo |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-08-08 |accessdate=2016-06-23 |archive-date=2012-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120812002329/http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/industry/record-labels/carly-rae-jepsen-claims-longest-hot-100-1007780352.story |dead-url=no }}</ref> 次周，歌曲銷量突破百萬大關。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/480425/flo-ridas-whistle-works-way-to-top-of-hot-100 |title=Flo Rida's 'Whistle' Works Way to Top of Hot 100 |first=Gary |last=Trust |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-08-15 |accessdate=2012-08-15 |archive-date=2013-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130329125406/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/480425/flo-ridas-whistle-works-way-to-top-of-hot-100 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2012年11月，在專輯《從月亮看世界》上榜之後，歌曲達到了第8的新高位。<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473967/rihanna-scores-double-domination-atop-hot-100-billboard-200 |title= Rihanna Scores Double Domination Atop Hot 100, Billboard 200 |first= Gary |last= Trust |publisher= Billboard |date= 2012-11-28 |accessdate= 2012-11-28 |archive-date= 2013-02-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130223022712/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473967/rihanna-scores-double-domination-atop-hot-100-billboard-200 |dead-url= no }}</ref> 次周，歌曲又上升至第7名，在后兩個月又分別跌至第8名和第9名。2013年1月中旬，歌曲又創造了第6名的新高位。<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1484103/bruno-mars-still-atop-hot-100-william-britney-spears-enter-top-10 |title= Bruno Mars Still Atop Hot 100, Will.i.am & Britney Spears Enter Top 10 |first= Gary |last= Trust |work= Billboard |date= 2013-01-09 |accessdate= 2016-06-23 |archive-date= 2013-02-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130202010856/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1484103/bruno-mars-still-atop-hot-100-william-britney-spears-enter-top-10 |dead-url= no }}</ref>  由於電台支持，2012年11月至2013年1月中旬期間歌曲每週平均新增了超過100,000單元銷量。<ref name="billboard_cover"/> 2014年3月，歌曲在美國銷量突破500萬大關。<ref>{{cite news |title=Chart Watch: Pharrell "Happy" Despite Oscar Loss |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/chart-watch-pharrell-happy-despite-oscar-loss-020930488.html |last=Grein |first=Paul |work=Yahoo Music |date=2014-03-05 |accessdate=2014-03-05 |archive-date=2014-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309043451/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/chart-watch-pharrell-happy-despite-oscar-loss-020930488.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 截至2015年12月，歌曲在美國共獲得了5,400,000份銷量。<ref name="us_sales">{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6805220/american-idol-final-season-cut-four-weeks-short|title=American Idol' Final Season To Be Four Weeks Shorter Than Last|date=2015-12-10|author=Michele Amabile Angermiller and Shirley Halperin|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2016-06-23|archive-date=2016-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425094327/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6805220/american-idol-final-season-cut-four-weeks-short|dead-url=no}} Sales figure given here [http://www.billboard.com/files/media/BB38-idol-01.jpg] {{Wayback|url=http://www.billboard.com/files/media/BB38-idol-01.jpg |date=20151211095945 }}</ref>

==音樂錄影帶==
歌曲的音樂錄影帶由约瑟夫·托曼導演，在2012年7月14日至16日拍攝完成。音樂錄影帶于2012年8月2日在飛力普的Vevo頻道首播，主色調為黑白，記錄了飛力普從[[丹佛|丹佛]]到[[鹽湖城|鹽湖城]]開展《美國偶像》巡迴演出的過程。導演談及音樂錄影帶的目的時說這個音樂錄影帶是為了“讓某些東西更加真實以展示飛力普是什麼樣的人”，“讓人有在家、靜謐的感覺，即便你真的遠離家門。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/american-idol-phillip-phillips-home-video-357872|title='American Idol' Winner Phillip Phillips Premieres 'Home' Video|date=2012-08-02|accessdate=2012-08-03|work=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Shirley|last=Halperin|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120804122918/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/american-idol-phillip-phillips-home-video-357872|archive-date=2012-08-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

